        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(pdf): guard native provider requests",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nRoute native Anthropic/Gemini PDF provider requests through OpenClaw's shared guarded provider HTTP path.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- Use `resolveProviderHttpRequestConfig` and `postJsonRequest` for native PDF provider POSTs.\r\n- Thread resolved model headers and provider request transport metadata from the PDF tool into native PDF helpers.\r\n- Replace successful provider `res.json()` parsing with bounded `readProviderJsonResponse` parsing.\r\n- Add focused regressions for private-network blocking, explicit `allowPrivateNetwork` opt-in, and oversized successful JSON responses.\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n\r\n- `corepack pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`\r\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.test.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-tool.test.ts`\r\n- `corepack pnpm format:check -- src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-tool.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.test.ts`\r\n- `corepack pnpm tsgo:core`\r\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --parallel-tests \"node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.test.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-tool.test.ts\"` clean, no accepted/actionable findings\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n- AI-assisted.\r\n- No `CHANGELOG.md` update.\r\n- `corepack pnpm check:changed -- src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-tool.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.test.ts` did not run checks because the delegated Blacksmith Testbox path failed at local `crabbox` binary sanity checks before executing the lane.\r\n",
